description:
First off, HUGE apology for going afk and not uploading AGAIN even though I said there would be videos for the weekend. I DID record the videos (G-Dash, horror game, cooking w/ Kenshin) but I didn't get to edit them. I THOUGHT I'd be able to edit during the nights at PAX, then of course we ended up getting into shenanigans and I wasn't able to. 

Consistency is obviously something I'm struggling with right now, can't seem to find that groove I used to have. But I am not going to give up, I'm just sorry to all those patiently waiting like, "where is this dude at?"

Anyway, these are our adventures or 'mis'adventures of PAX South 2016, DEFINITELY best PAX experience I've had so far. Thank you to all those that made my experience better including:

FIRSTLY ALL OF THE SAMURAI I GOT TO MEET :)
